summary: Antennaria is a beautiful, overgrown cavern temple home.
descriptionHtml:
Antennaria is a beautiful, overgrown cavern temple home.

There are no requirements. Fully navmeshed and safe to store your valuables. There are loads of Mannequins and Weapon Racks! A gorgeous bedroom, bathing area, alchemy lab and your own skyforge equivalent. The home opens up to a massive tower atop a mountain peak with stunning views of Skyrim.

Antennaria is located just past the Valtheim Towers at the giant waterfall. (Head downriver from Whiterun and you\'ll find it)
